'''Laramus Base''' was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] base on the planet [[Laramus]] in the [[Laramus system/Legends|Laramus system]]. It was destroyed by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces and the surviving troops went on to form the [[Laramus Base Irregulars]].

